Demo web application of the PRISM system. Demonstrating some of the key features releases of Java EE 7 and Spring MVC 3.2.

- Java EE 7: Input bean validation (including custom validator) using JSR(349) reference implementation Hibernate Validator 5.0.1.Final 
- Spring MVC 3.2 Exception handling using @ControllerAdvice annotation 
- Validate against XSS using @SafeHtml validator 
- RESTful/JSON services using Spring MVC 3.2 
- Tomcat7 Maven Plugin Config

Additional features to be added include: 
-Java EE 7: Websocket 1.0 in 
-Java EE 7: JMS 2.0 suport for Spring
